(45216, 1, '2011-07-31 00:01:09', '2011-07-31 06:01:09', '[Brightcove Video]1701073860001[/Brightcove Video]Wayne Klein is a financial fraud expert and founder of Klein &amp; Associates, PLLC. As a court-appointed attorney receiver, Klein takes over companies that have been operating Ponzi schemes or other investment frauds.  He reconstructs their financial transactions, files lawsuits to recover monies paid improperly to insiders, sells assets, and distributes the recovered funds back to the victims.  One of the cases for which he is acting as Receiver is the Trigon case in Idaho Falls, Idaho, where $68 million was taken in a Ponzi scheme.', 'Wayne Klein', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wayne-klein', '', '', '2014-06-30 14:37:07', '2014-06-30 20:37:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ldp/htdocs/?p=45216', 0, 'post', '', 0),
