(45222, 1, '2011-08-14 00:01:18', '2011-08-14 06:01:18', '[Brightcove Video]1701185448001[/Brightcove Video]Les Pico is the Executive Director of Player Development and Legal for the Minnesota Vikings. He is directly involved with personal welfare and legal issues that arise concerning players, coaches and staff.  Other areas of expertise and responsibilities included in his career include implementing player programs to assist with continuing education, family assistance and career internships.  He assists the personnel staff by evaluating and interviewing players at the NFL Combine and assists in evaluations during pro free agency. Les is involved with the administration of the annual rookie symposium that is attended by all NFL drafted rookies.', 'Les Pico', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'les-pico', '', '', '2014-06-30 14:37:06', '2014-06-30 20:37:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ldp/htdocs/?p=45222', 0, 'post', '', 0),
