(45438, 1, '2013-03-17 00:01:36', '2013-03-17 06:01:36', '[Brightcove Video]2137158444001[/Brightcove Video]“Maria is President of her own company, M.L. Pribyl and Associates, and co-founder of The Tech Mentors Company. She is past President of the award winning BYU Management Society Silicon Valley Chapter and Past President of the Silicon Valley Women’s organization (affiliated with the BYU Management Society). She is a senior-level professional computer software instructor and consultant for several training companies in Silicon Valley with 20+ years of training experience. She has conducted training for clients such as Cisco Systems, NVidia, SanDisk and Stanford University. Maria also serves as 1st Counselor in the Relief Society of her ward.”', 'Maria Pribyl', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'maria-pribyl', '', '', '2014-06-30 14:36:08', '2014-06-30 20:36:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ldp/htdocs/?p=45438', 0, 'post', '', 0),
