(45635, 1, '2014-07-02 13:23:36', '2014-07-02 19:23:36', '\r\n\r\nDavid A. Christensen is a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints and has served as president of the Chile Santiago North Mission and the Guatemala City Missionary Training Center. He recently took early retirement from his decades-long work on the Brigham Young University-Idaho religion faculty and is currently associated with the school as adjunct faculty while he pursues writing and humanitarian work in Honduras.', 'David A. Christensen', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '45481-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-02 13:23:36', '2014-07-02 19:23:36', '', 45481, 'http://www.latterdayprofiles.org/45481-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
